这些商店可能会出现什么问题——如果没有零售业务，它们并不总是受到与传统同行相同的审查。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/mrbeast-sues-his-fast-food-chain-for- sell-inedible-burgers-203055288.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/mrbeast-sues-his-fast-food-chain-for-selling-inedible-burgers-203055288.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 38e6cbd1-8ff0-4f39-bc43-5900cf67e44a</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 20:30:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690921856</ingested><modified> 2023-08-01T20:31:00+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="2526" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7941c950-309c-11ee-bd97-dae317869f8c" width="3600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2526" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7941c950-309c-11ee-bd97-dae317869f8c" width="3600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Dave Kotinsky via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[EAST RUTHERFORD, NEW JERSEY - SEPTEMBER 04: Global YouTube star MrBeast (R) poses with fan at the launch of the first physical MrBeast Burger Restaurant at American Dream on